{
  "stem": "13213.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I stayed there for a couple days and I didn't like it there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I met a friend that was in a orphanage from HaNoar HaTzioni.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I went there and I stayed in Cracow for about four or five months.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I couldn't sit still, so I went to work in a library.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Actually, not in a library.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It's like a bookstore, and I was delivering books.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "People were buying books and I was delivering the books.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then, I-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from Cracow, they moved us to Bytom, a city in upper Silesia, Poland, where we were in a-- called, like, a kibbutz, or a kinderheim, orphanage.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And in there, I went and registered to go to school in [INAUDIBLE] school, which was a trade school and a regular schooling-- high school courses.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I took my courses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I did very well in the school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The people were very nice to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "The principal was a Communist Jew, but he was very good.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "He was dedicated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And when we-- when I finished, I got my certificate as a machinist and auto mechanic.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "After I finished this course, a friend of mine was going to school in a city of Gliwice, also in Poland.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And that was a special school-- pre-university school where younger men that didn't have a chance during the war to finish high school in a normal way, they would prepare you in one year to go to university.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I went over and registered.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And fortunately, at that time, the principal was a Jewish man by the name of Mr.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Friedman.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "His wife was a math teacher, and they were without any children and they took to me very much, and they were very nice to me.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
